    /*
* This overrides Chrome's default autofill colors.
* This is fragile as Chrome likes to update this value out of nowhere with no forward warning.
* See: https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=935991
* See: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/2781549/removing-input-background-colour-for-chrome-autocomplete
*/
